WARNING: THESE SCRIPTS WILL ALTER YOUR FILES. PLEASE ENSURE YOU HAVE A BACK UP!!!!


Basically this is a bunch of scripts to help fix your audio files. 
Each script tries to do just one task in keeping with linux methodology.

License: No license, do with it as you wish. Always appreciate contributions.


